r67GKkA8_childItem_7","label":"gg5r67GKkA8_childItem_7","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Can I pay on delivery?</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKeQeBypCw_text","label":"ggKeQeBypCw_text","default":"<p>Right now, it’s online only on our official website and Amazon.</p><p>If you see it somewhere else, it may not be original.</p><p>Retail pharmacy availability is coming soon.</p><p>If you own a pharmacy, contact us at info@serlinolab.it.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggE2a9V-meS_text","label":"ggE2a9V-meS_text","default":"<p>Men who want their face actually clean and ready for whatever they’re putting on next.</p><p>This washes off dirt, oil, sweat, and buildup<br>so your cream or serum can actually do its job.</p><p>Works for all skin types.<br>Dry. Oily. Somewhere in between.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBr_m71saN_text","label":"ggBr_m71saN_text","default":"<p>Because water doesn’t cut it.</p><p>Water won’t remove oil, pollution, dead skin, or the junk your face collects all day.</p><p>A real cleanser does.</p><p>Clean skin absorbs products better.<br>Which means better results. Faster.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2xFSx-IzP_text","label":"gg2xFSx-IzP_text","default":"<p><strong>Step 1:</strong><br>2–3 pumps on a wet face</p><p><strong>Step 2:</strong><br>Rub in with circular motions</p><p><strong>Step 3:</strong><br>Rinse. Dry off. Done.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglFYYGZwgb_text","label":"gglFYYGZwgb_text","default":"<p>Use it before shaving.</p><p>It softens your skin and facial hair so the razor glides easier.<br>Less irritation. Cleaner shave.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLoiQJZLr1_text","label":"ggLoiQJZLr1_text","default":"<p><strong>Niacinamide</strong><br>Helps improve skin elasticity.<br>Reduces excess pigment.<br>Helps fade dark spots.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Chamomile</strong><br>Calms irritated skin.<br>Great after shaving.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Sodium Hyaluronate</strong><br>Helps your skin hold onto moisture — even after you rinse.<br>So you feel clean. Not dried out.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPeIVTKzHi_text","label":"ggPeIVTKzHi_text","default":"<p>No.</p><p>Unlike basic bar soap, this doesn’t strip your skin raw.</p><p>Niacinamide and Chamomile help keep your skin balanced and comfortable.</p><p>Clean — not tight.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZpTGwlLBy_text","label":"ggZpTGwlLBy_text","default":"<p>Yes.</p><p>You’ll get your order in 24–48 hours.<br>Pay cash when it shows up.</p>"}],
